---
title: Mushroom Gravy-Smothered Striploin with Roasted Potatoes and Grilled Asparagus
description: Fire up the grill and get ready to BBQ!  With lemony asparagus, herby mushroom gravy and Montreal steak spiced-striploin, this dinner is packed full of fresh, summer flavours.
